{"tid":845713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國客疑爭食雞鯁死 網民：一人一盤就唔使搶","createTime":"2018-10-03T01:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T08:27:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9a10aefe8806a85a17c58636589385b401fdfc5e","tid":845713,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538470931_8137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538470931_8137.jpg&h=16ff3cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名中國遊客昨日在泰國春武里府一處餐廳用餐時，疑似因為吃雞的速度太快，雞骨頭卡在喉嚨不幸鯁死。<br />\n<br />\n據《泰國頭條新聞》在官微報道，泰國春武里府警察局接到餐廳老闆報案，稱有一名31歲中國男遊客在他的餐廳吃飯，不幸被雞骨鯁死，警方抵達事發地點調查後得知，該遊客跟其他6名同伴點了一盤雞來吃，可能是吃的速度太快，導致雞骨卡住喉嚨，無法呼吸，經搶救無效。<br />\n<br />\n有網民就猜測，事主之所以食雞鯁死，是因為與人爭食，「嘴巴還會動呢，一人點一盤就不用搶着吃了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181003/58748070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58748070&d=vafsAJtW1FASTd9W%2FbGZwp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5e2b6634\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58748070&h=3b4752b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181003/58748070</a>"},{"pid":"a0c51c2d30cb25145874b81600aca1082ccc9fd2","tid":845713,"uid":38049,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:20:24.000Z","msg":"以為你講打機"},{"pid":"d2668ddb96e82380a2410a991e880deb64d34f11","tid":845713,"uid":146604,"like":131,"dislike":0,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:22:05.000Z","msg":"大吉大利 今晚食雞"},{"pid":"ddf904a6980de59b17be03cefb704c6ee7e5cd71","tid":845713,"uid":49974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2668ddb96e82380a2410a991e880deb64d34f11","tid":845713,"uid":146604,"like"